{"tid":2499864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本駐澳洲大使稱日本應加入“五眼聯盟”","createTime":"2021-04-22T08:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T08:39:20.000Z","uid":294518,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e1499b603b147c9ccba2d2ff6ba135477e4ac4ac","tid":2499864,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:06:57.000Z","msg":"日本駐澳洲大使稱日本應加入&ldquo;五眼聯盟&rdquo;<br />\nJapan should join Five Eyes intelligence network, says ambassador<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.smh.com.au/world/asia/japan-should-join-five-eyes-intelligence-network-says-ambassador-20210420-p57kv6.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smh.com.au%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fjapan-should-join-five-eyes-intelligence-network-says-ambassador-20210420-p57kv6.html&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5Clnfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=b85e51d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.smh.com.au/world/asia/japan-should-join-five-eyes-intelligence-network-says-ambassador-20210420-p57kv6.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaAuGSYzWx88vTcfcTjCTWCC3fzB7EFWUrFLkGRsDb3fw?filename=Oot7R5c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOot7R5c.png&h=b7b3600e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e74639c4678131e38d6235fd4d9d791f9d8a986b","tid":2499864,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:08:22.000Z","msg":"據2020年12月上任的日本駐澳洲大使山上信吾（Shingo Yamagami）說，日本正在朝著加入&ldquo;五眼聯盟&rdquo;的方向取得進展。 <br />\n<br />\n山上信吾說：&ldquo;我對不久的將來感到非常樂觀。希望看到這個想法在不久的將來成為現實&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;五眼聯盟&rdquo;是英語國家二戰後建立的的情報網絡，通過持續的、最高機密的交流相互分享電子情報。澳洲和新西蘭在1956年加入了由美國、英國和加拿大建立的情報網。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲國立大學國家安全學院院長梅德卡夫（Rory Medcal）說：&ldquo;就利益和能力而言，日本是最佳人選。如果有一個國家對中共國有細微的瞭解，那麼日本就是。日本擁有自己的大量情報收集和評估能力。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n就在新西蘭外交部長馬胡塔（Nanaia Mahuta）表示，對擴大五眼集團的職權範圍&ldquo;感到不舒服&rdquo;的時候，日本成為&ldquo;第六只眼&rdquo;的想法越來越受到重視。<br />\n<br />\n曾任日本外務省情報部門負責人的山上信吾，在接受《悉尼先驅晨報》和《時代報》採訪時表示，這六個國家都是民主國家，都將中共國視為戰略對手。<br />\n<br />\n日本是美國的長期條約盟友，擁有美國的主要軍事基地。<br />\n<br />\n山上信吾說，日本要加入&ldquo;五眼聯盟&rdquo;，需要東京在改善日本的情報界和立法方面，做大量的準備，這將是一個&ldquo;重大的體制挑戰&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"347fd4f2acf36b739e577d50fac01fbed45620d7","tid":2499864,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:08:59.000Z","msg":"五目連合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb31c6085b49719cedc18a5056396e78e6567ba","tid":2499864,"uid":16057,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:09:48.000Z","msg":"踢走紐西蘭 <br />\n日本取代"},{"pid":"eae7a8a04cc51e809e5498d8076595a81904461d","tid":2499864,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:11:27.000Z","msg":"日本唔係anglo-saxon <br />\n點比你入呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3600c78757935ad06f7000825aca05f25ce2288","tid":2499864,"uid":270220,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:12:19.000Z","msg":"取代New Xi Land <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7919249fa97daad4e5d40d03f8046b147fd6e370","tid":2499864,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWVy6CFCNMnXB8VkBvoQYpKqqys8TZ4TcbejYhP9XdYzB?filename=PWYGWz1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWYGWz1.png&h=5252ad1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYihx62xc1fYWFFbbmYqVwCdmYmR5B82Vc396hGsWxHGB?filename=xuEbzmG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxuEbzmG.png&h=99a9896d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNbHiAEU5opk91ZWPtuQ6xtxr14eicK4ijPqHFEdQYAHK?filename=72uSiOp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72uSiOp.png&h=5c2135eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qm